Method Detail

meshInto

public void meshInto(Element2D e,
                     int m,
                     int n)
Meshes quad area elements into same type elements as the original one.

Parameters:
e - Two dimensional quad element to be meshed. Element should be a quad element and is not checked. It should be checked before assigned to function!!
m - The number of divisions in local eps1 direction. This should be at least 1 and is not checked. It should be checked before assigned to function!!
n - The number of divisions in local eps2 direction. This should be at least 1 and is not checked. It should be checked before assigned to function!!
